      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 11,
      "message": "I wanted to do this one as I have a value for it already but I can't figure out how to get portal-mariadb.config.mariadbRootPassword in this portal-widget context (without re-declaring it in this chart)....  It is also stored in a K8s secret.  Can we reference a K8s secret in a config map flat source file?",
